                <mxCell id="n_gap_note" value="GAP: state machine writes the SAME PK/SK as the&#xa;real SESSION item. No Wait / task token — all 6&#xa;states (CREATED...COMPLETED) run in one execution&#xa;within ~1s of exam start, immediately stamping&#xa;status=COMPLETED. auth-validator then denies every&#xa;subsequent answers/session/submit call, since it&#xa;requires STARTED/IN_PROGRESS. See docs/async-stack.md." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;strokeColor=#B85450;fillColor=#FBEEEE;fontColor=#B85450;fontSize=10;align=left;spacingLeft=6;fontStyle=2;" parent="1" vertex="1">
